with fixes from espie@@.
ok espie@@ general mumbling of approval of others.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
#	$OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.12 2005/04/28 21:30:13 espie Exp $
d7 1
a7 1
libstdc++-v3 ../usr.bin/cc/libobjc
d13 2
a14 1
SUBDIR+=libiberty libreadline libstdc++-v3 ../usr.bin/cc/libobjc
@


1.12
log
@also use new libobjc on old architectures, since it builds fine with
gcc 2.95.

tests and okay miod@@, marc@@.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
#	$OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.11 2004/03/01 02:52:11 drahn Exp $
a3 1
USE_GCC3?=No
d6 2
a7 1
SUBDIR+=libiberty libobjc libstdc++ ../egcs libreadline libf2c
d9 1
a9 1
.  if ${USE_GCC3:L} == "yes"
d11 3
@


